# HOCAI System v2.1 — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete knowledge tracking system that runs **parallel to the IDE**, automatically capturing and synthesizing technical knowledge from AI conversations.

### Architecture
```
Antigravity (IDE Agent) → HTTP POST → HOCAI Server (localhost:8000) → SQLite DB + AI API
```

---

## Server Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [main.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/main.py) | FastAPI app + 8 API routes |
| [database.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/database.py) | SQLite + SQLAlchemy (WAL mode) |
| [models.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/models.py) | 4 ORM tables (shared concepts) |
| [schemas.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/schemas.py) | Pydantic request/response |
