| [graph.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/graph.py) | Edge management + score propagation |
| [synthesizer.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/synthesizer.py) | AI lesson synthesis + quality-gated updates |
| [config.py](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/config.py) | Environment config |
| [start_hocai.bat](file:///d:/HOCAISYSTEM/hocai-server/start_hocai.bat) | Manual startup script |

